Flappadiddle - Amiga Edition

Flappy's on a quest to land on as many of the ominous floating platforms
that it can.  As the dangerous spikes and even more menacing balls of
lava continue to thwart Flappy's attempt, how far will it manage to flap
before the end of its three lives.

